    "Html": "\r\n<p>Hi All,</p>\r\n<p>There is a formatting bug in the shopping cart that causes the line item sub total to not display currency decimal places if the total is an even dollar value.</p>\r\n<p>Here is the fix that I'll integrate into the next release version.</p>\r\n<p>Change the &quot;Item Total&quot; template as follows.<span style=\"font-family:Consolas; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; font-size:x-small\"></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; color:#0000ff; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; color:#0000ff; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; color:#0000ff; font-size:x-small\">&lt;</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; color:#800000; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; color:#800000; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; color:#800000; font-size:x-small\">ItemTemplate</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; color:#0000ff; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; color:#0000ff; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; color:#0000ff; font-size:x-small\">&gt;</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; font-size:x-small\"></p>\r\n<p>&lt;%<span style=\"font-family:Consolas; color:#0000ff; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; color:#0000ff; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; color:#0000ff; font-size:x-small\">#</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; font-size:x-small\">\r\n (</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; color:#2b91af; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; color:#2b91af; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; color:#2b91af; font-size:x-small\">Convert</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; font-size:x-small\">.ToDouble(Eval(</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; color:#a31515; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; color:#a31515; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; color:#a31515; font-size:x-small\">&quot;Quantity&quot;</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; font-size:x-small\">))\r\n * </span></span><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; color:#2b91af; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; color:#2b91af; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; color:#2b91af; font-size:x-small\">Convert</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; font-size:x-small\">.ToDouble(Eval(</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; color:#a31515; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; color:#a31515; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; color:#a31515; font-size:x-small\">&quot;UnitCost&quot;</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; font-size:x-small\">))).ToString(</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; color:#a31515; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; color:#a31515; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; color:#a31515; font-size:x-small\">&quot;N2&quot;</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; font-size:x-small\">)%&gt;</span></span></p>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:Consolas; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; font-size:x-small\"><font face=\"Consolas\" size=\"2\">\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; font-size:x-small\"></span></p>\r\n</font></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; color:#0000ff; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; color:#0000ff; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; color:#0000ff; font-size:x-small\">&lt;/</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; color:#800000; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; color:#800000; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; color:#800000; font-size:x-small\">ItemTemplate</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; color:#0000ff; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; color:#0000ff; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; color:#0000ff; font-size:x-small\">&gt;</span></span></span></span></span></span>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n",
